title: Ed Schultz Show - June 27, 2008 (48kbs Audio).mp3
description:
Friday on The Ed Schultz Show!

Norman Goldman our Senior Legal Analyst fills in for Big Eddie.

Paul Helmke, President of the Brady Campaign joins the 1st hour of Friday\&#039;s show to discuss the Supreme Court decision on the 2nd Amendment.

Ray Schoenke of the American Hunters and Shooters Association joins the 2nd hour of Friday\&#039;s show to discuss the Supreme Court vote on the 2nd Amendment.

Norman will have your calls and the latest news! 

Also try listening to Thom Hartmann,  Mike Malloy,  Randi Rhodes and Jeff Farias
